snippet.description:
Hi I'm Chris and I'm a chemistry phd student with a love for scientific instrumentation!

Mostly chromatography and particle spectroscopy. Design and construction of scientific instruments, spectrometers and such.

Feel free to send me an email! 
Stick around!
